{"tid":131343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"差佬：我哋被迫害緊，被德國納粹軍隊迫害緊我哋猶太人呀，啱唔啱呀","createTime":"2017-02-23T04:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T08:41:34.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e864a3d2f346a48b71d1dae4726e153f4a93c0f","tid":131343,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"昨晚4個警察協會聯合舉行的「特別代表大會」，商討為淪為七犯的七警籌款等支援工作。集會期間，有警員上台發言時表示，「我形容就係我咃依家就係第二次世界大戰，我哋係猶太人，我哋被迫害緊，被德國納粹軍隊迫害緊我哋猶太人呀，啱唔啱呀」，全場即回答「係！」該言論惹來不少抨擊，法政匯思召集人任建峰在fb轉載報道後指「這是對六百萬名猶太死難者的極度不敬」，並提到他曾去過奧斯威辛屠殺營，曾有逾110萬猶太人在該集中營遭到屠殺；任建峰強調「納粹迫害猶太人真的不可亂用作比喻」、「俾人鬧同俾人滅族是兩回事」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言諷刺警員的言論，「被迫害既猶太人可以打完人又有人工出」、「點解可以無知識到咁既程度」、「市民冇用毒氣焗你地喎」；有人呼籲網民去信以色列駐香港領事館投訴，以譴責相關言論，並附上領事館電郵地址（ info@hongkong.mfa.gov.il ）。<br />\n七警早前被裁定「襲擊致造成身體傷害」罪成，被判入獄2年，而辯方的資深大律師駱應淦也認為刑期不算過重，惟不少撐警人士仍感不滿。"},{"pid":"3826b45e7842ce22f572cd9c8f13fcceac2751fa","tid":131343,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責德國 要求道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b10795c3c60651560bbcaad9d8ed3d5efec3df","tid":131343,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"去信領士館link?"},{"pid":"82803e35b3ed4f51121af7334fc31c1761acd30e","tid":131343,"uid":21064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"警隊要求獨立 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時復國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a6990853be5709d31a05d875af1f574e12675e","tid":131343,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"偽進仔咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9c413b56d433412ef43526cc9e08e51684d4f4","tid":131343,"uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"班差佬short撚左？<br />\n德國人尤太人都唔會亂講<br />\n你班差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cbbda3370d86d8e7c521576203d24735d8156a","tid":131343,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"扮猶太人又收將香港市民比喻做納粹既稅做人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5be747dd8dd0d76c2dc27a6cbb03e72b1983591","tid":131343,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/73741/-七警案-有片-集會警-社會對警隊心態-如二戰時猶太人被逼害\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F73741%2F-%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%8D%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B-%E5%A6%82%E4%BA%8C%E6%88%B0%E6%99%82%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E5%AE%B3&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e6698ca6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/73741/-七警案-有片-集會警-社會對警隊心態-如二戰時猶太人被逼害</a><br />\n<br />\n一人一信比以色列同各猶太受難組織知道呢班知法犯法垃圾，抽人地民族大傷口既笑話！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：支持請正評長推，Thanks！！！<br />\n</span></strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/085213_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F085213_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3ad9315d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>俾埋七警打人條片俾大使館睇, 問下當年係唔係七個猶太人打一個立粹黨先至俾人大屠殺???</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非常好！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/094241_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F094241_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f0759be5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cc97b90d312aa151a9afa7ff6cdf054155ad040","tid":131343,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班差佬short撚左？<br />\n德國人尤太人都唔會亂講<br />\n你班差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成件事反映d差佬都係癲癲地<br />\n都唔知自己係執法者犯法會好大鑊<br />\n仲以為自己比人屈⋯<br />\n律師政府幫你搵埋<br />\n費用又係政府幫你比埋<br />\n洗唔洗政府幫你坐埋呀差佬<br />\n成班都鳩下鳩下咁"},{"pid":"ec6bc196aa71af8c6a28aedfa4c1422e967b1df9","tid":131343,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人開始寫信? 冇嘅話一陣試下獻醜<br />\n<br />\n集中 post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/131109/page/6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/131109/page/6</a>"},{"pid":"a87c19f328dde5b9578d99eac2047b87ca43d040","tid":131343,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170223/large/1487834389_8a35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170223%2Flarge%2F1487834389_8a35.jpg&h=d50a0468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港猶太大屠殺及寬容中心教育總監李家豪，對於有警員自比「被納粹德軍逼害的猶太人」感詫異，認為反映對這場歷史浩劫不了解、欠尊重。他指出，第二次世界大戰中，一共超過600萬名猶太人被屠殺，而逼害猶太人的乃有系統、有國家在背後支持的政權，屠殺手段包括送到「滅絕營」中，利用毒氣室等手段殺害，質疑發言警員所指被「納粹德軍」逼害，跟史實有何可類比之處，以及「納粹德軍」在現實中代表何方、何人。<br />\n<br />\n李家豪指，今早得悉居港的猶太人社群，對相關警員言論有反響，主要是感到詫異。他表示難以代表社群回答有否覺得不受尊重，惟有一點可以肯定，就是猶太人要求尊重史實，盼望國際了解他們被逼害的事實。<br />\n<br />\n李又分享指，昨晚看到新聞片段時，正值他製作關於大屠殺的教材，最令他感驚詫的，是發言者詢問同僚是否認同有如猶太人般被逼害時，台下竟「一呼百應」。<br />\n<br />\n李家豪續指，該中心每年舉辦多項公眾教育活動，包括到大學、中學及國際學校演講，亦會舉辦相關電影節，以及每年邀請僅餘的大屠殺倖存者來港分享。他表示，大部分活動均對公眾開放，歡迎任何人包括警方參與。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚4個警察協會集會期間，有警員上台發言時表示，「我形容就係我咃依家就係第二次世界大戰，我哋係猶太人，我哋被迫害緊，被德國納粹軍隊迫害緊我哋猶太人呀，啱唔啱呀」，全場即回答「係！」</blockquote>"}]}